                  <rs id="t18640201-239-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18640201-239-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18640201-239-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, Unlawfully uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
